Source code license
============================================================================================
Before version 1.0, Pubwich was released under a Creative Commons BY-SA[1] license. However,
since version 1.0, Pubwich source code is released under the open-source GPL 2.0[2] license,
which means that you can use and modify the code freely (even for commercial use). However,
if you want to distribute your modified code, you must release it under the same license.


External libraries
============================================================================================
Cache_Lite, Savant3, PHP Gettext, PHP Markdown and PHP Smartypants libraries are included
with their respective licenses.


